1. Font weirdness with Arial: Arial font interpretation is buggered in KDE.
   Hack solution:

   - Remove Arial fonts via KDE Font Installer.
   - Add Helvetica font from LaTeX. (I copied 
     /usr/share/doc/liblo-0.18/latex/Helvetica.ttf from sunball.) That way,
     sites that request Helvetica get a True-Type one.
